OL,3,C'I was Mrs Bothwell for nine hours':
OL,4,CWife thanks hospice for perfect last
OL,5,Cday
OL,7,FAlex Spiceley talked to wife Alison
OL,8,Fabout their last day together...
OL,10,FA woman has thanked the team at Jersey
OL,11,FHospice Care for creating the perfect
OL,12,Flast day for the love of her life.
OL,14,FAfter knowing each other for 24 years,
OL,15,FDavid and Alison Bothwell were married
OL,16,Flast Thursday (15 August) in the
OL,17,Fgarden at Jersey Hospice, where he had
OL,18,Fbeen receiving end of life care.
OL,20,FSadly David died nine hours later.
