OL,3,C'I was Mrs Bothwell for nine hours':
OL,4,CWife thanks hospice for perfect last
OL,5,Cday
OL,7,FHis wife Alison said: "It didn't
OL,8,Fmatter how long we had - the first
OL,9,Ftime he called me Mrs B was wonderful.
OL,11,F"I think perhaps it was the last
OL,12,Fimportant thing he wanted to do.
OL,14,FAlison added: "We just decided to get
OL,15,Fmarried at the last minute, and almost
OL,16,Fwas the very last minute.
OL,18,F"I was Mrs Bothwell for nine hours.
OL,19,FBut it was the most perfect, wonderful
OL,20,Flast day on planet earth".
