OL,3,C'I was Mrs Bothwell for nine hours':
OL,4,CWife thanks hospice for perfect last
OL,5,Cday
OL,7,FKerry Huelin from Jersey Hospice cared
OL,8,Ffor David in his final days, and said:
OL,9,F"I was so privileged to play even a
OL,10,Flittle part in it. They were a
OL,11,Fbeautiful couple and David was so
OL,12,Ffunny.
OL,14,F"There was so much laughter in that
OL,15,Froom when he was getting ready that
OL,16,Fmorning. He was a joy to look after,
OL,17,Fhe really was".
