OL,3,C'I was Mrs Bothwell for nine hours':
OL,4,CWife thanks hospice for perfect last
OL,5,Cday
OL,7,FIn a statement, the charity said: "At
OL,8,FHospice, our motto is 'live life to
OL,9,Fthe full' - and we strive to make sure
OL,10,Fwe help our patients and their loved
OL,11,Fones do just that.
OL,13,F"It was an honour and a privilege for
OL,14,Four team to put on Ali and David's
OL,15,FWedding".
